<div class="page-header">
  <h1>âœï¸ Create New Post</h1>
  <p>Share your knowledge with the community</p>
</div>

<div class="content">
  <div class="form-container create-post-form">
    <% if (error) { %>
    <div class="error-message">
      <p>âŒ <%= error %></p>
    </div>
    <% } %>

    <form method="POST" action="/posts" class="post-form">
      <div class="form-group">
        <label for="title">Post Title:</label>
        <input
          type="text"
          id="title"
          name="title"
          required
          placeholder="Enter an engaging title for your post"
        />
      </div>

      <div class="form-group">
        <label for="content">Post Content:</label>
        <textarea
          id="content"
          name="content"
          rows="15"
          required
          placeholder="Write your post content here. You can use line breaks to create paragraphs.

For example:
This is the first paragraph of your post.

This would be the second paragraph.

Share your insights, tutorials, or thoughts!"
        ></textarea>
      </div>

      <div class="form-group">
        <label for="authorId">Author:</label>
        <select id="authorId" name="authorId">
          <option value="1">Admin</option>
          <option value="2">John Doe</option>
          <option value="3">Jane Doe</option>
        </select>
        <small>ğŸ’¡ Demo: Select who should be credited as the author</small>
      </div>

      <div class="form-actions">
        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">ğŸ“ Publish Post</button>
        <a href="/posts" class="btn">Cancel</a>
      </div>
    </form>
  </div>

  <div class="writing-tips">
    <h3>âœ¨ Writing Tips</h3>
    <div class="tips-grid">
      <div class="tip-card">
        <h4>ğŸ“‹ Structure</h4>
        <p>
          Start with an introduction, develop your main points, and conclude
          with key takeaways.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="tip-card">
        <h4>ğŸ¯ Focus</h4>
        <p>
          Keep your post focused on one main topic or concept for better
          readability.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="tip-card">
        <h4>ğŸ“ Formatting</h4>
        <p>
          Use line breaks to separate paragraphs. Keep sentences clear and
          concise.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="demo-info">
    <h3>ğŸ§ª Demo Features</h3>
    <p>This create post form demonstrates:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>
        <strong>Form Validation:</strong> Required fields and error handling
      </li>
      <li><strong>Data Processing:</strong> Controller processes form data</li>
      <li>
        <strong>Model Creation:</strong> New Post instance created and stored
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Redirect Flow:</strong> Successful creation redirects to new
        post
      </li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      <small
        >ğŸ’¡ Posts are stored in memory and will reset when server
